<?php
/* @var $this SiteController */

$this->pageTitle=Yii::app()->name;
?>

<h1>Welcome to our application:</i></h1>
<p>This is an application dedicated to use the components  of Yii . This components will be used to query the Sakila database in 
different fashions.</p>


<ul>
	<li>There will be brief descriptions for the use of the features of the application:</li>
	  <li>Most of the commands will be used by routing after the index.php of the site </li>
	  <li>Following is a list of commands and what is achieved after executing the command</li>
<li> http://localhost/application/index.php?r=film </li>	 
<p> This will let us see the results for a Film Model - related to the film table - created with the CRUD utility of Yii. </p>
<li> http://localhost/application/index.php?r=grid/aR </li>
<p> This will let us see the results of Film Model according to the Active Record class of Yii. </p>
<li> http://localhost/application/index.php?r=grid/array </li>
<p> Corresponds to an array that has already been pre-configured in the application </p>
<li> http://localhost/application/index.php?r=grid/sql </li>
<p> Corresponds to a direct query in the database, in this case in the table film. </p>
</ul>

<?php

?>
